ary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Latinized version of a Continental Germanic name, a short form of various compound women's personal names derived from <i>berht</i> ‘famous’ (akin to Modern English <i>bright</i>). It probably existed in England before the Conquest, and was certainly reinforced by Norman use, but fell out of use in the 15th century. It was reintroduced into the English-speaking world from Germany in the 19th century, but has once again gone out of fashion."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Bertha de Gudenborc was born about 1209, in Wolfhagen, Kassel, Hesse, Germany. She married Arnold I. Wolf von Gudenberg about 1228, in Wolfhagen, Kassel, Hesse, Germany. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1230, at the age of 22."},"et":{"Abt 1209–1230":"umbes 1209–1230","1196–Male":"1196–Surnud","1229–1286":"1229–1286","1209–1230":"1209–1230","um 1229":"umbes 1229","1286":"1286","1230":"1230","1196":"1196","Abt 1209":"umbes 1209","1209":"1209","Abt 1228":"umbes 1228","1229":"1229","Of Wolfhagen, Hessen, Germany":"Wolfhagen, Kreis Kassel, Hessen, Saksamaa","Wolfhagen, Kassel, Hessen.":"Wolfhagen, Kreis Kassel, Hessen, Saksamaa"},"fi":{"Abt 1209–1230":"noin 1209–1230","1196–Male":"1196–Kuollut","1229–1286":"1229–1286","1209–1230":"1209–1230","um 1229":"noin 1229","1286":"1286","1230":"1230","1196":"1196","Abt 1209":"noin 1209","1209":"1209","Abt 1228":"noin 1228","1229":"1229","Of Wolfhagen, Hessen, Germany":"Wolfhagen, Kreis Kassel, Hessen, Saksa","Wolfhagen, Kassel, Hessen.":"Wolfhagen, Kreis Kassel, Hessen, Saksa"},"fr":{"Abt 1209–1230":"environ 1209–1230","1196–Male":"1196–Décédé","1229–1286":"1229–1286","1209–1230":"1209–1230","um 1229":"environ 1229","1286":"1286","1230":"1230","1196":"1196","Abt 1209":"environ 1209","1209":"1209","Abt 1228":"environ 1228","1229":"1229","Of Wolfhagen, Hessen, Germany":"Wolfhagen, Kreis Kassel, Hessen, Allemagne","Wolfhagen, Kassel, Hessen.":"Wolfhagen, Kreis K